{
  "texts": [
    "g, When interacting with an accurate algorithm, AI-induced accuracy increases over time (n = 50).",
    "h,i, Participants perceived the influence of the accurate algorithm on their judgements to be greatest (h; n = 120), even though the actual influence of the accurate and biased algorithms was the same (i; n = 120).",
    "The thin grey lines and circles correspond to individual participants.",
    "In d and f, the circles correspond to group means, the central lines represent median values and the bottom and top edges are the 25th and 75th percentiles, respectively.",
    "In e and g, the error bars represent s.e.m."
  ]
}